                <p>We collect data such as IP address, browser type, transaction history, and site interactions for security and analytics.</p>

                <h4><strong>Mobile</strong></h4>
                <p>Most mobile devices allow you to disable location services in the settings menu.</p>

                <h4><strong>Information from Other Sources</strong></h4>
                <p>We may receive verification data from third parties to prevent fraud.</p>

                <h4><strong>Information You Can Access</strong></h4>
                <p>You can access details like recent transactions, personal information, payment settings, and email notifications.</p>
              <% } else { %>
